02:26.790 --> 02:30.820
Yeah. After a while,the family
got defensive, stopped cooperating.

02:30.830 --> 02:35.160
A bit like the-- what's her
name? The jon-benet case, i guess.

02:35.170 --> 02:36.880
I never liked them for it,anyway.

