I always figured it was
somebody outside the home.

02:41.900 --> 02:43.440
What's the bureau's
interest in the case?

02:43.460 --> 02:46.350
Um,research.

02:46.360 --> 02:47.650
Is this everything?

02:47.670 --> 02:49.480
There might be another
box down in records.

02:49.500 --> 02:52.660
I'd like to see it
all, if you don't mind.

03:01.120 --> 03:03.840
Lots of luck,everybody, let's go.

