03:35.430 --> 03:38.780
Uh,breaking into my room and
watching "days of our lives."

03:38.790 --> 03:40.240
"young and the restless."

03:40.260 --> 03:42.280
aren't you supposed to be
on a plane back to d. C. ?

03:42.290 --> 03:44.470
You're supposed to be
hanging out with your mom.

03:44.480 --> 03:47.040
And you're not.

03:47.790 --> 03:48.650
Riley jenkins?

03:48.660 --> 03:50.730
No,it's not-- that's
actually not why i'm here.

03:50.740 --> 03:52.510
Reid?

03:52.520 --> 03:54.400
Come on,man.

03:54.410 --> 03:57.090
Who do you think you're talking to?

03:57.950 --> 04:00.100
I know what this has been doing to you.

04:00.120 --> 04:01.500
Let us help.

04:01.510 --> 04:05.350
Maybe together we can
find out who killed him.

04:06.170 --> 04:07.780
I think i might already know.

04:07.790 --> 04:09.740
So,tell us about the suspect.

